abstract.text: Create and manage notes and to-do list items.

legalNotices.copyright: Copyright © 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.

inlineContent.text: With the lists and notes domain, users can create to-do lists, mark to-do list items as complete, or ask Siri to create or modify notes in their favorite note-taking app. When creating items in a to-do list, the user may also ask you to set up a reminder based on the user’s location or a specific date. Your intents app extension takes the information provided to it and creates the corresponding tasks, notes, and reminders either directly in your app or by communicating that information to your servers.
